snippet.title: Rock Band Blitz - Announce Trailer
snippet.description: Blitz is a downloadable rhythm game featuring controller-based gameplay in line with the developer's PlayStation 2 classics Amplitude and Frequency that benefits from cross-compatibility with Rock Band's existing music catalogue.
